{
  "stem": "7069.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as it turned-- as it was-- it turned out that some guy behind me hollered, hey, guys, look.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Turn around.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I turned around, and I saw what I still consider the most beautiful sight of my life-- a contingent of American armored vehicles coming down the hillside with the American insignia on it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And our guards, of course, at that moment, took off in all directions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Stopped short at a moment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The commander of the American outfit stopped in front of us and directed us back to the-- to the one road which-- where there was an American Red Cross contingent.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He says, it's just a quarter of a mile up that one road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There they are there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We are waiting for you already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sorry we couldn't come any sooner to you, he said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so-- and so-- and he made a remark which sounded to us utterly-- utterly ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He says, now, anybody that wants to walk that quarter mile, just go that way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Not this or that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we said, my gosh, walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, otherwise there will be trucks and jeeps to pick you up, don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyways, but while these vehicles were coming by, they were shooting out of their turrets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were actually a fighting contingent, fighting the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are shooting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But while they were riding by and shooting, they opened the hatches, and threw out all kinds of ration boxes, the military ration boxes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, we all ran as much as we could and grabbed one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you could see some guys just-- as I, too, tried to open it right away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some guys opened it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And regretfully-- some guys opened it, I meant to say, and ate everything inside.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
